        "content": "<p>I was trying to undersand <code>omega</code> better and wanted to define a <code>Justification</code>based  on the pretty-printed trace output:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kn\">import</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">Lean</span>\n\n<span class=\"kd\">set_option</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">trace.omega</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">true</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">theorem</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">foo</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≥</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">3</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">_</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≥</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">5</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">x</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">+</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">y</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"bp\">≥</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"mi\">8</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">:=</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"kd\">by</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"n\">omega</span>\n\n<span class=\"c\">/-</span><span class=\"cm\"> includes:</span>\n\n<span class=\"cm\">[omega] Justification:</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">    [0, 1] ∈ ∅: combination of:</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">    • [0, 1] ∈ (-∞, 4]: tidying up:</span>\n<span class=\"cm\">      • [0, -1] ∈ [-4, ∞): 1 * x + -1 * y combo o